        "action": "Ban all forms of public nudity except for emergency reasons",
        "additional_details": "I would like the Government to do this as I believe it can cause mental harm to adults and children, as well as the fact that I believe it is degrading to humans on a whole. I am concerned public nudity means it cannot be controlled who sees them and children who are meant to be protected and safeguarded may be exposed to seeing adult genitalia.",
        "background": "I would like the Government to pass a law which completely bans all forms of public nudity.",
